---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Medical Services — Primary, Urgent &amp; Pediatric Care | AymanCare"
  description="Primary care, walk-in urgent care, pediatrics, allergy treatment, weight loss programs, flu care and COVID-19 testing at four Dallas–Fort Worth clinics."
>
  <Fragment slot="head">
  <script type="application/ld+json" is:inline set:html={"{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"BreadcrumbList\",\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":1,\"name\":\"Home\",\"item\":\"https://aymancare.com/\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":2,\"name\":\"Services\",\"item\":\"https://aymancare.com/services/\"}]}"} />
  </Fragment>
<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="breadcrumbs fade-in">
    <a href="/">Home</a><span class="sep">✦</span><span>Services</span>
  </div>
  <h1 class="page-title fade-in">A full range of care,<br>for <em>every stage.</em></h1>
  <p class="page-subtitle fade-in">From pediatrics to senior care. Our mission is to help you maintain a high quality of life through best health practices — delivered with warmth and modern medical rigor.</p>
  <div style="display: flex; gap: 10px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 32px;" class="fade-in">
    <span class="pill">All ages welcome</span>
    <span class="pill pill-accent">Medicare & Tricare</span>
    <span class="pill pill-outline">Walk-ins accepted</span>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section" style="padding-top: 0;">
  <div class="svc-list-wrap">
    <a href="/services/primary-care/" class="svc-row fade-in">
      <span class="sr-num">N° 01</span>
      <span class="sr-title"><em>Primary</em> Care</span>
      <span class="sr-desc">Comprehensive preventive physicals, chronic condition management, and a long-term partner for your family's health journey. We accept most major insurance including Medicare and Tricare.</span>
      <span class="sr-cta">Learn more <span class="sr-arrow">↗</span></span>
    </a>
    <a href="/services/walk-in-urgent-care/" class="svc-row fade-in">
      <span class="sr-num">N° 02</span>
      <span class="sr-title"><em>Walk-in</em> Urgent Care</span>
      <span class="sr-desc">Same-day care without an appointment. For acute illness, minor injuries, COVID-19 testing, and the unexpected turns a day can take. Most visits begin within 30 minutes.</span>
      <span class="sr-cta">Learn more <span class="sr-arrow">↗</span></span>
    </a>
    <a href="/services/pediatric-care/" class="svc-row fade-in">
      <span class="sr-num">N° 03</span>
      <span class="sr-title"><em>Pediatric</em> Care</span>
      <span class="sr-desc">Pediatric experts providing personalized, child-centered care at every stage of growth — colds, strep, asthma, allergies, skin conditions, and more. Gentle, unhurried, family-first.</span>
      <span class="sr-cta">Learn more <span class="sr-arrow">↗</span></span>
    </a>
    <a href="/services/flu-treatment/" class="svc-row fade-in">
      <span class="sr-num">N° 04</span>
      <span class="sr-title"><em>Flu</em> Symptoms</span>
      <span class="sr-desc">Board-certified physicians work closely with PAs and nurse practitioners to diagnose and treat the flu quickly — so you can feel better faster, and protect the people around you.</span>
      <span class="sr-cta">Learn more <span class="sr-arrow">↗</span></span>
    </a>
    <a href="/services/allergy-treatment/" class="svc-row fade-in">
      <span class="sr-num">N° 05</span>
      <span class="sr-title"><em>Allergy</em> Treatment</span>
      <span class="sr-desc">Pollen, dust mites, mold, stings, or food — we examine, test, and bring forth the best solutions for lasting relief, so your year doesn't have to be defined by symptoms.</span>
      <span class="sr-cta">Learn more <span class="sr-arrow">↗</span></span>
    </a>
    <a href="/services/weight-loss/" class="svc-row fade-in">
      <span class="sr-num">N° 06</span>
      <span class="sr-title"><em>Weight</em> Loss</span>
      <span class="sr-desc">Medically-supervised weight loss programs focused on building your body's health and improving your habits — so you can enjoy life, not just fit into clothes.</span>
      <span class="sr-cta">Learn more <span class="sr-arrow">↗</span></span>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="employer-section">
  <div class="employer-inner fade-in">
    <div>
      <span class="overline">◆ For Employers</span>
      <h2>Occupational medicine<br>& <em>employer services.</em></h2>
      <p>We offer a variety of Occupational Medicine services for employers — on-site or in-clinic — at reasonable cost.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="tier-wrap">
      <div class="tier-box">
        <h4><em>On-site</em></h4>
        <ul>
          <li>Vaccine administration</li>
          <li>Drug screening</li>
          <li>Pre-employment physicals</li>
          <li>DOT physicals</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="tier-box">
        <h4><em>Injury</em> care</h4>
        <ul>
          <li>Work-related injuries</li>
          <li>Workers' comp docs</li>
          <li>Return-to-work evals</li>
          <li>Case management</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="tier-box">
        <h4><em>Preventive</em></h4>
        <ul>
          <li>Comprehensive exams</li>
          <li>Lab panels & diagnostics</li>
          <li>Health assessments</li>
          <li>Wellness visits</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="big-cta" style="padding: 100px 40px;">
  <div class="big-cta-inner">
    <span class="overline fade-in">◆ Not sure what you need?</span>
    <h2 class="fade-in">Let's figure it<br>out <em>together.</em></h2>
    <p class="fade-in">Call us, walk in, or book online — we'll help you find the right next step.</p>
    <div class="cta-row fade-in">
      <a href="/book-online/" class="btn btn-primary">Book appointment →</a>
      <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-outline">Call your nearest clinic</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
</Base>
